A Quick Summary

0. Run ./install-pre-commit.sh
   Note, this will perform the following checks:
     o Make sure every applicable file has licensing
     o Make sure every commit is signed-off-by
     o Make sure every commit passes make check

1. Configure and build RefFS:
   o cd where-you-want-to-build-reffs
   o mkdir build
   o cd build
   o ../reffs/configure
   o make [-j]
   o make check

Note, to switch to gcc:

make -f Makefile.precommit build -- --with-cc=gcc
